# Security Flags

Flag and fix these patterns:

- passwordHash or tokens in packages/shared or API responses
- Frontend importing apps/api or @prisma/client
- Missing validation on POST/PATCH/PUT DTOs
- Protected routes without JwtAuthGuard
- NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix missing on client-exposed env vars
- Raw entity returned from controller (must use shared response type)

Run pnpm doctor after fixes.
